      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KAELIX COMET (7) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when second (25.56) at Warrnambool. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Can find winning form. MR. KIA ORA (8) should get a clear run from the wide draw. Safely held last start when a 11 length 6th at this track (22.69). Form here at this distance is strong including one wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. FRED'S FURY (3) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at Warrnambool in a handy 22.28 beating Seats Two. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure.",
